OL,6,FThe Toffees were hit with a 10-point
OL,7,Fdeduction after an independent
OL,8,Fcommission found they had exceeded
OL,9,Fpermitted losses under the league's
OL,10,Fprofitability and sustainability rules
OL,11,F(PSR) by #19.5million over an
OL,12,Fassessment period ending with the 2021-
OL,13,F22 season.
OL,15,FFollowing the deduction, saying they
OL,16,Fwere "shocked and disappointed by the
OL,17,Fruling" and believed "the sanction is
OL,18,Fdisproportionate and wholly unjust".
