OL,6,FThe club later lodged a formal appeal
OL,7,Fto the independent commission, and had
OL,8,Fbeen waiting since December for the
OL,9,Foutcome.
OL,11,FNow, after a three-day hearing in
OL,12,FFebruary, an independent Appeal Board
OL,13,Fhas cut the deduction by four points,
OL,14,Fwhich moves the club on to 25 points
OL,15,Fin the table and up to 15th place.
OL,17,FIn response to the outcome, Everton
OL,18,Fsaid they were "satisfied" with the
OL,19,Freduction in points.
