OL,6,FThey said: "While the Club is still
OL,7,Fdigesting the Appeal Board's decision,
OL,8,Fwe are satisfied our appeal has
OL,9,Fresulted in a reduction in the points
OL,10,Fsanction."
OL,12,FThe appeal board, comprising of Sir
OL,13,FGary Hickinbottom (Chair), Daniel
OL,14,FAlexander KC and Katherine Apps KC,
OL,15,Fupheld two of the nine grounds the
OL,16,Fclub appealed on.
OL,18,FEverton's appeal related to the
OL,19,Fsanction, rather than the fact of the
OL,20,Fbreach, which the club admitted.
