OL,6,FThe Toffee's statement continued: "The
OL,7,FClub is also particularly pleased with
OL,8,Fthe Appeal Board's decision to
OL,9,Foverturn the original Commission's
OL,10,Ffinding that the Club failed to act in
OL,11,Futmost good faith.
OL,13,F"That decision, along with reducing
OL,14,Fthe points deduction, was an
OL,15,Fincredibly important point of
OL,16,Fprinciple for the Club on appeal. The
OL,17,FClub, therefore, feels vindicated in
OL,18,Fpursuing its appeal.
