OL,6,F"Notwithstanding the Appeal Board's
OL,7,Fdecision, and the positive outcome,
OL,8,Fthe Club remains fully committed to
OL,9,Fcooperating with the Premier League in
OL,10,Frespect of the ongoing proceedings
OL,11,Fbrought for the accounting period
OL,12,Fending in June 2023."
OL,14,FThe league referred Everton to the
OL,15,Fcommission in March for an alleged
OL,16,Fbreach of its profitability and
OL,17,Fsustainability rules in the period
OL,18,Fending in the 2021-22 season.
