OL,6,FThe rules allow clubs to lose a
OL,7,Fmaximum #105million over a three-year
OL,8,Fperiod or face sanctions.
OL,10,FThe appeal board's summary said
OL,11,FEverton relied on nine grounds of
OL,12,Fappeal against the initial 10-point
OL,13,Fsanction, seven of which related to
OL,14,Fhow the original commission dealt with
OL,15,Fvarious mitigating and aggravating
OL,16,Ffactors.
OL,18,FThose seven were dismissed but the
OL,19,Fappeal board did conclude on the other
OL,20,Ftwo grounds that the original
OL,21,Fcommission made legal errors.
