OL,6,FThe appeal board found the original
OL,7,Fcommission was wrong in finding
OL,8,FEverton had been "less than frank" in
OL,9,Frelation to what they told the Premier
OL,10,FLeague about debt linked to their new
OL,11,Fstadium, and finding that in being so
OL,12,Fthe club had breached a league rule
OL,13,Frequiring an obligation to act in
OL,14,Futmost good faith.
OL,16,FWhile Everton's representations
OL,17,Fregarding the stadium were found to be
OL,18,Fmaterially wrong, it was not the
OL,19,FPremier League's case that that was
OL,20,Fanything other than an innocent
OL,21,Fmistake.
