OL,6,FThe appeal board also found it was
OL,7,Fwrong of the commission not to take
OL,8,Finto account available benchmarks for
OL,9,Fsanction, such as EFL guidelines.
OL,11,FFollowing today's announcement,
OL,12,FLiverpool Metro Mayor Steve Rotheram -
OL,13,Fwho has consistently voiced his
OL,14,Fdisappointment at the original
OL,15,Fpunishment - said in a statement:
OL,17,F"The Premier League's culture of
OL,18,Fsecrecy has done nothing to foster
OL,19,Fconfidence or trust."
